s.'=>'此 LoginPress 外掛程式可讓您（管理員）為您不想提供密碼登入您網站的特定使用者產生唯一的 URL。此 Pro 外掛程式為您提供了已提供自動產生的登入連結的所有使用者的清單。您可以停用某些人的存取權限並刪除某些使用者。','This LoginPress add-on lets you change the login page URL to anything you want. It will give a hard time to spammers who keep hitting to your login page. This is helpful for Brute force attacks. One caution to use this add-on is you need to remember the custom login url after you change it. We have an option to email your custom login url so you remember it.'=>'此 LoginPress 外掛程式允許您將登錄頁面 URL 更改為您想要的任何內容。這將給不斷點擊您的登錄頁面的垃圾郵件發送者帶來困難。這對於暴力攻擊很有説明。使用此外掛程式的一個警告是，您需要在更改自定義登錄 URL 後記住它。我們可以通過電子郵件發送您的自訂登錄網址，以便您記住它。','You have a lifetime license, it will never expire.'=>'您有終身許可證，它永遠不會過期。','Your (%2$s) license key is valid until %1$s.'=>'您的 (%2$s) 許可證金鑰有效期至 %1$s。','Your license key has been expired on %1$s.'=>'您的許可證密鑰已於 %1$s 過期。','You need to upgrade to LoginPress Pro to access these add-ons.'=>'您需要升級到 LoginPress Pro 才能訪問這些載入項。','%s Something Wrong.'=>'%s 出了點問題。','Your License Key isn\'t valid'=>'您的許可證密鑰無效','Activating %s...'=>'正在啟動 %s...','%s Activated.'=>'%s 已啟動。','Deactivating %s...'=>'正在停用 %s...','%s Deactivated.'=>'%s 已停用。','Something went wrong in loading the Add-Ons, Try again later!'=>'載入附加元件時出錯，請稍後再試！','UPGRADE NOW'=>'現在更新','Extend the functionality of LoginPress with these awesome Add-ons'=>'通過這些令人敬畏的附加元件擴展 LoginPress 的功能','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit this item.'=>'抱歉，您無權編輯此項目。','Password'=>'密碼','Confirm Password'=>'確認密碼','%1$sError:%2$s Please enter your password twice.'=>'%1$s錯誤：%2$s 請輸入兩次密碼。','%1$sError:%2$s Passwords doesn\'t match.'=>'%1$s錯誤：%2$s 密碼不匹配。','Error: %s'=>'錯誤：%s','You have already set your own password, use the password you have already set to login.'=>'您已經設定了自己的密碼，請使用您已經設定的密碼登入。','Uninstall'=>'解除安裝','Activate Plugin'=>'啟動插件','Install'=>'安裝','You need to activate your license to download the following add-ons.'=>'您需要啟動許可證才能下載以下載入項。','Buy %s now'=>'立即購買 %s','Buy Now'=>'立即購買','Analytify'=>'Analytify','Analytify is reshaping Googl